About sachin

Ramalinga Reddy has been the pillar of Karnataka politics and has contributed to the states progress for over 40 years. He has dedicated most part of his life for the service of the people of Karnataka. He is an accessible, simple, humble, trusted, accountable and experienced leader. He is available at his home office at Lakkasandra every day from 8:00 am where he listens to the problems of the people patiently and ensures that their problems are solved as soon as possible. He has always supported cultural programmes and festival celebrations in his constituency.
